<p>Yasemin Vargı Emirdağ is a board member at MV Holding. She also served at several NGO boards including TED Istanbul College, Contemporary Istanbul Young Advisory Council as well as Mind Your Waste Foundation, an organization founded in 2015 to create a clean and sustainable world by promoting behavioral change in society.</p>
<p>Having started her career as an Art Director, Yasemin has curated several art projects for hotel and office spaces over the years, promoting social awareness through art. In addition, she has been the Chief Editor of ArtSpeak.NYC, a digital platform on the Contemporary Art in New York.</p>
<p>Mrs. Emirdağ received her BS in Communications at University of Miami in 2008 and also holds a masters degree in Modern and Contemporary Art from Christie’s in London.</p>